FIRST THE UBUNTU INSTALLATION: 
konsta@Konstas-MBP ~ % docker run -it ubuntu

AFTER THAT, CURL INSTALLATION:
root@5f70f228f262:/# apt-get update; apt-get install curl

AND THEN THE EXERCISE:
root@5f70f228f262:/# sh -c 'echo "Input website:"; read website; echo "Searching.."; sleep 1; curl http://$website;'
Input website:
helsinki.fi
Searching..
